---

<BaseLayout
  title="BreederHQ vs Breeder Cloud Pro: The Honest 2026 Comparison"
  description="BreederHQ vs Breeder Cloud Pro on pricing, species, marketplace, buyer portal, and OFA Sync. Publicly verifiable facts. Compare side by side."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
  faqs={faqs}
>
  <script is:inline type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(articleSchema)} />
  <script is:inline type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(competitorReviewGraph)} />

  <a href="#main-content" class="skip-link sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:absolute focus:top-4 focus:left-4 focus:z-50 focus:px-4 focus:py-2 focus:bg-white focus:text-black focus:shadow-lg focus:rounded">
    Skip to content
  </a>

  <main id="main-content">
    <nav class="breadcrumb py-4 px-4 bg-gray-50" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-sm">
        <li><a href="/" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Home</a></li>
        <li class="text-gray-400">›</li>
        <li><a href="/compare" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Compare</a></li>
        <li class="text-gray-400">›</li>
        <li aria-current="page" class="text-gray-600">BreederHQ vs Breeder Cloud Pro</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">BreederHQ vs Breeder Cloud Pro: The Honest 2026 Comparison</h1>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Published: July 1, 2026 &middot; Last verified against breedercloudpro.com: July 1, 2026</p>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Breeder Cloud Pro is the mature multi-species records tool at a low monthly price. BreederHQ is a broader platform (records, marketplace, buyer flow, automation, native mobile) at a higher price. Both are used by real breeders. Here is the honest version of when each wins.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-md bg-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] text-white font-semibold hover:bg-[hsl(24,95%,48%)] transition">
            Start 14-day free trial
          </a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-300 text-gray-900 font-semibold hover:border-gray-400 transition">
            See BreederHQ pricing
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TL;DR -->
    <section class="py-12 px-4 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <aside class="bg-white border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] p-6 rounded shadow-sm" role="complementary" aria-label="Page summary">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">TL;DR</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong>Pick Breeder Cloud Pro if</strong> monthly line-item cost is your primary constraint and you want a 30-day trial that spans a full breeding milestone. The trade is monthly price for the operational and buyer-facing surface BreederHQ ships. Right tool for a records-and-pedigree-first program that only needs a directory listing on the buyer side.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Pick BreederHQ if</strong> you want to run the program AND present it to buyers from one system: nine species in one account, a transactional marketplace at marketplace.breederhq.com, OFA Sync (automatic pull of public results), CHIC Readiness Widget, Scout AI that reads lab PDFs into records, rules-based automation across the offspring lifecycle (born to listing-live to waitlist-opens to deposit-collected), and an embed widget that keeps your own website in sync with your listings. The 14-day trial is shorter and the entry price is higher. The trade is feature scope for cost.
          </p>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Screenshot placeholder callout -->
    <section class="py-8 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <figure class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8 bg-gray-50 text-center">
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">Illustration</div>
          <div class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium">BreederHQ dog record with OFA Sync results displayed inline</div>
          <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-3">A dog record in BreederHQ showing hip, elbow, cardiac, patella, and DNA results pulled automatically from OFA once the registration number is entered. Same data propagates to pedigrees.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Comparison table -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Side-by-side: BreederHQ vs Breeder Cloud Pro</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Publicly verifiable facts only, sourced from breedercloudpro.com and breederhq.com. Verified July 1, 2026. Vendors change pricing and feature scope. Confirm on each site before committing.
        </p>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead class="bg-gray-100 text-left">
              <tr>
                <th scope="col" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Capability</th>
                <th scope="col" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Breeder Cloud Pro</th>
                <th scope="col" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">BreederHQ</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Entry price</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">$6.99/mo Standard, $13.99/mo Pro, $130/yr Pro annual</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">See <a href="/pricing" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">pricing page</a>. FOUNDER50 code: 50% off Pro or Enterprise for 12 months (first 100 founders).</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Free trial length</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">30 days</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">14 days</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Species supported</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">7 (dog, cat, horse, goat, rabbit, sheep, small animals)</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">9 (dogs, cats, horses, goats, rabbits, sheep, alpacas, llamas, cattle)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Public buyer-facing surface</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">"Find a Breeder" directory at breedercloudpro.com/breeders</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Transactional marketplace at marketplace.breederhq.com</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Buyer portal</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Pet Portal: pet details, contracts, invoices, payments</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Per-buyer client portal: records, photos, pedigree, contracts, invoices, direct messaging, documents</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">OFA Sync (automatic)</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Not publicly advertised</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Yes: enter reg #, results appear on the record and pedigree</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">CHIC Readiness Widget</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Not publicly advertised</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Yes: breed-specific required tests, on-file status, missing gaps</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">AI document extraction</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Not publicly advertised</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Yes: Scout AI has dedicated parsers for Embark and OFA, plus generic vet-invoice and lab-PDF extraction that handles other providers (Wisdom Panel, UC Davis, GenSol, Paw Print, and unlisted labs) through Claude-based document reading</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Camera receipt-to-expense</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Not publicly advertised</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Yes: point mobile camera at receipt, Scout files vendor/date/amount/category to ledger</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Rules-based automation</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Not publicly advertised</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Yes: offspring-born to listing-live to waitlist-opens to deposit-collected</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Website embed widget</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Not publicly advertised</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Yes: live listings syndicate to Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, Shopify, GoDaddy, HTML</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Printable identification cards (kennel cards, cage cards, stall cards, pen cards)</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Not publicly advertised</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Yes: species-aware ID card generator across all 9 species with species-appropriate fields (last vaccination and heartworm for dogs, last farrier and coggins for horses, last kindling for rabbits, and so on)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Rearing protocol library</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Not publicly advertised</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Yes: 9 shipped system protocols across neonatal and socialization stages (ENS, ESI, Handling Habituation, Volhard Puppy Aptitude Test, Crate Introduction, Rule of 7s Socialization, Sound Desensitization, Gun Conditioning) plus the BreederHQ Gun Dog Development Program (Day 3 through Day 364, 64 activities), plus custom breeder-authored protocols, plus an opt-in community library. Every protocol carries a liability acknowledgment.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Mobile</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">iOS and Android apps + web</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Native iOS and Android apps + responsive web (<a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/breederhq/id6761625868" rel="nofollow noopener" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">App Store</a> / <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.breederhq.mobile" rel="nofollow noopener" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Google Play</a>)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Public scale claims</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">17,000+ breeders, 110,000+ animals, 95,000+ Pet Portals, 48,000+ litters/breedings (self-reported)</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Growing; founder-led; not disclosed publicly</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Founded</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">2015</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">2026</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row" class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-left">Founder-led</th>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Yes</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Yes</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-4">
          <strong>Last verified:</strong> July 1, 2026 against breedercloudpro.com/pricing, breedercloudpro.com/features, and breederhq.com/pricing. Vendors change pricing and feature scope. Verify before you commit. Corrections: <a href="mailto:support@breederhq.com" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">support@breederhq.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What breeders say -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">What Breeder Cloud Pro users actually say</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Direct quotes from Capterra and SoftwareAdvice reviews of Breeder Cloud Pro. Not our characterization. Cited to the reviewer with a link to the source.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <blockquote class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-gray-300">
